Mnh Dn Thot Cng CGV
27.050 thnh vin
Cho mng n vi ngi nh chung ca nhng thanh nin FA tham gia chng trnh i 1 V 2 ti CGV. Hy gi nhng tm s, tnh cm ca bn CGV s tr thnh cu ni cho bn v crush. Hy mnh dn thot cng CGV nh! Cc bn lu mt s ni quy sau nh: Admin s t chi duyt cc post c ni dung r r n cc a im nu khng phi l rp chiu phim CGV hay cc ni khc nm ngoi s qun l ca CGV. Chng mnh mun to mi trng giao lu, kt bn v thn thin nhm gn kt cc bn c thn m in nh ti CGV. Khi cc bn hn h n nhng a im khc nm ngoi phm vi qun l ca CGV bn mnh s khng th m bo cc yu t ny, do cc bi ny s khng c duyt. Khi ng gp g, cc bn nn cnh gic, tm hiu k i phng, khng nghe li r r g gm. Admin s thng tay t chi duyt cc post ng ti hnh nh c nhn nhm mc ch cu view, cu like, cu followers, subscribers hoc cc mc ch khng ph hp khc. Cc bi ng hnh nh c nhn vui lng ng km cc thng tin c bn v bn nh tn, khu vc sinh sng, i tng bn mun xem phim cng, rp phim, tn phim, sut my gi. Admin s t chi duyt cc ni dung chia s mang tnh cht tiu cc. CGV l cu ni, to iu kin cc bn c thn m in nh gp g, n gn nhau hn. Tuy nhin, thnh i thnh cp th cn ph thuc cc yu t. Nu nh cha th thnh i, CGV hy vng bn ng nn v xem y l tri nghim mi bn chun b cho n "mt na" thc s. Hy gi nim tin vo cuc sng v chng ta ri ai cng s gp c mt na ca mnh. Admin s khng duyt cc bi post c ni dung hnh nh tri vi thun phong m tc Vit Nam, cc hnh nh mang tnh khiu gi, nhy cm v c th hay khoe khoang chi tiu, ti sn. Vui lng add hashtag #DiMotVeHai #henhoxemphim vo cc bi post r r xem phim hay #other vo cc post c ni dung khc admin d qun l v ngi khc d tm.
